Robert Fleming names strcutured finance director . Investment bank Robert Fleming & Co said on Thursday it has appointed Simon Davis as a director in its structured finance team . Davis will be based in Singapore and be responsible for developing the structured finance capability of Jardine Fleming , Fleming ' s joint venture with Jardine Matheson . Davis was previously at Rabobank in London and will report to Marcus Stanton who heads the structured finance team . - Joe Ortiz , London Newsroom + 44 171 542 8864 . 
